{"tid":2315493,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"RM「台灣國旗並列五星旗」延燒！中國網民竟開罵周子瑜","createTime":"2020-12-07T08:28:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T14:09:56.000Z","uid":16659,"like":163,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"3be9b4d8fce075e3c0d74b50bfa9efe5ce1cc995","tid":2315493,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T08:28:23.000Z","msg":"南韓綜藝節目「Running man」（RM）自2010年播出迄今紅遍全球，更多次在亞洲地區舉辦巡迴粉絲見面會，吸引不少粉絲前往朝聖。然而近日播出最新一集的節目中，卻因為「將我國國旗及中國國旗並列」而意外觸動了中國網民敏感的神經。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/07/2922751-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F07%2F2922751-PH.jpg&h=bad64ef5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲這一幕觸動了對岸網民敏感的愛國神經。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\nRM最新一集節目中玩起「大富翁」，地圖上除了地名以外也標註了所屬的國家及國旗，台北的區塊顯示「青天白日滿地紅國旗」，而旁邊竟剛好是「五星旗」的北京。瞬間讓觀看盜版影片的中國網民理智斷線，紛紛痛批RM製作組「淨搞些敏感的」。<br />\n<br />\n對此，不少中國網民揚言抵制RM主持群未來在中國的所有活動，甚至連代言的商品也連帶拒買，吶喊「國家面前無偶像」。另外，似乎是由於RM紅遍全球再加上敏感的國家議題，「RM」在微博的關鍵字熱度甚至一度在前5名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/07/2922753-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F07%2F2922753-PH.jpg&h=e2baf734&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲中國網民喊國家面前無偶像。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n此外，RM這次在節目中展露青天白日滿地紅國旗，對岸愛國網民除了要求道歉外，還將2016年韓國知名女團Twice的台灣成員周子瑜的「國旗事件」翻出，令人反感。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/07/2922755-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F07%2F2922755-PH.jpg&h=0a0f3d77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/07/2922756-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F07%2F2922756-PH.jpg&h=93ed5b76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲中國網民將周子瑜4年多前的國旗事件翻出。（圖／翻攝自微博）"},{"pid":"bd6809983700027d92244ba503b3e1644bcd7646","tid":2315493,"uid":368098,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T08:29:32.000Z","msg":"垃圾支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4fae32473723c36476a1b78f8a5eb8e18918b21","tid":2315493,"uid":320204,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T08:30:30.000Z","msg":"支那人收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d8bf4e5b3648a745cc340047065de39a0121c0","tid":2315493,"uid":16659,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"e4fae32473723c36476a1b78f8a5eb8e18918b21","tid":2315493,"uid":320204,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T08:30:30.000Z","msg":"支那人收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T08:31:07.000Z","msg":"支那人死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51556ae7e84c2cf481f915e13c5c3e63296d89db","tid":2315493,"uid":16659,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"quote":{"pid":"bd6809983700027d92244ba503b3e1644bcd7646","tid":2315493,"uid":368098,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T08:29:32.000Z","msg":"垃圾支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T08:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rWVYDjy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrWVYDjy.gif&h=7e224947&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97684933b7a0b32b4f78c7baf6c9f49179bd406f","tid":2315493,"uid":149494,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T08:31:34.000Z","msg":"痴線，隔咗咁多年都唔肯放過子瑜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經比佢地害到好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8551a39db62d5687816964ce78ae4a4f77bca5ec","tid":2315493,"uid":261849,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T08:31:50.000Z","msg":"岩岩ig 都見到<img src=\"/assets/fac